title: Wayne resident crowned Miss New Jersey USA
text:
Wayne resident crowned Miss New Jersey USA October 22, 2015 Last updated: Thursday, October 22, 2015, 1:21 AM The Record — Christina Joseph 
PAGEANT: Wayne woman is crowned Miss New Jersey USA 
Wayne resident Jessielyn Palumbo, 23, was crowned Miss New Jersey USA 2016 on Sunday at the Hilton Parsippany Hotel. She will compete this summer for the Miss USA title. Palumbo, a 2010 graduate of Wayne Hills High School and 2014 graduate of The College of New Jersey, works as a freelance photographer and runs her own fashion and beauty photography studio.
